stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR

    [*] --> Initializing

    Initializing --> Idle : self-test passed
    Initializing --> Fault : startup failure

    Idle --> Tightening : armed by angler
    Tightening --> Armed : tension at setpoint
    Tightening --> Idle : disarmed during tighten

    Armed --> BiteDetected : tension spike<br/>(> bite_threshold)
    Armed --> Tightening : slack detected<br/>(tension < setpoint - hysteresis)
    Armed --> Idle : disarmed

    BiteDetected --> SettingHook : after hook_set_delay
    BiteDetected --> Armed : tension dropped<br/>(false bite within delay)

    SettingHook --> Reeling : tension confirmed<br/>(fish on after sharp pull)
    SettingHook --> Armed : tension dropped<br/>(missed strike — bait still on?)

    Reeling --> Landed : line fully in<br/>(reel-encoder at limit)
    Reeling --> Fault : line slack OR motor stall

    Landed --> Idle : angler reset

    Idle --> Fault : fault event
    Armed --> Fault : fault event
    Reeling --> Fault : fault event

    Fault --> Idle : fault cleared + reset

    note right of Armed
        Holding line at setpoint;
        watching for bite spike.
    end note

    note right of BiteDetected
        Brief delay (configurable):
        let fish swallow before
        setting the hook.
    end note

    note right of Reeling
        Slow controlled reel-in
        to land the fish.
    end note
